        Create a new reply to a request to instantiate an MX plugin.
        Parameters:
        token - the token given by the application to match this asynchronous reply to the request.
        mxpInstanceID - the assigned instance ID.
        pluginID - the plugin ID for the plugin that was instantiated.
        success - whether the plugin was successfully instantiated.
        msg - an informational message about the outcome of the instantiate request.
